{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 2927302, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 556656, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "有一个特征值为0", "timestamp": 1636791903, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2927304, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 556656, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "因为如果行列式不等于0，可以构造出来它的逆矩阵", "timestamp": 1636791923, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2927332, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 556656, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "因为不可逆矩阵主元列不够，一定存在一个列向量可以由其他列向量线性组合表示，这样其列向量张成的多边体的“体积”一定为0，也就是行列式为0", "timestamp": 1636792192, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2927367, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 556656, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "一个矩阵和它的逆矩阵的行列式互为倒数，如果不可逆，那说明行列式为0", "timestamp": 1636792549, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2927374, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 556656, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "以上表述全部等价", "timestamp": 1636792659, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2928105, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 556656, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "有一点要注意，数值计算中存在精度误差，所以行列式不是判定可逆与否的绝对标准。绝对标准是奇异值。来自研究生课程矩阵分析与应用。", "timestamp": 1636798976, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 5, "pid": 556656, "reply": 6, "tag": null, "text": "为什么不可逆矩阵的行列式等于0？线代渣渣在线求救", "timestamp": 1636791861, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1636798977, "url": "", "vote": {}}}